  <trk>
    <name>BCN-L3 — Andorra Weekend Loop — Day 2</name>
    <desc>Deploy from BCN and ride into the Andorra. Hit Manresa and La Seu d&apos;Urgell. Loop back to BCN over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
